			<div class="content" id="post-content-4333952">
									

<p>Woot woot, a parawatch thingy. This story was inspired by <a href="/scp-2915">SCP-2915</a> (which, I believe, makes the twist a little bit more obvious), a couple of other creepypastas I've read in the past and one of the levels from <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/356670/Spookys_Jump_Scare_Mansion/">this game</a> (check it out it's good). Thanks all of you for reading!</p>
<p><strong>Cool crit people:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580838543" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;">The Great Hippo</a></span> <strong>(<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/tower-b">Tower-B</a>)</strong></li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4483018); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580838543" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4483018); return false;">TheMightyMcB</a></span> <strong>(<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/another-soul-joins-the-halkost">Another Soul Joins The Halkost</a>)</strong></li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4894577); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4894577&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580838543" alt="Laneous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4894577)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4894577); return false;">Laneous</a></span> <strong>(<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/cuteness-on-main">Cuteness on main!</a>)</strong></li>
