			<div class="content" id="post-content-4343388">
									

<p>This was certainly engaging. Especially the descriptions of eating, they actually made me a little squeemish.<br />
I only have two minor nitpicks.</p>
<p>Having a person remind the OP to bring their phone to take some pictures, only for the OP to <em>not</em> do so feels like an odd choice. It almost feels like that one comment could just be removed, but I can see the value in having a slightly-too-eager word of encouragment from crilasxowe.</p>
<p>My other nitpick is suuuper minor, but the OP's description of the voice in the basement, specifically the &quot;such desparation, such agony&quot; part feels a bit over-dramatic, but that could just be me.</p>
<p>Still, +1 from me</p>

